{
  "id": "adv_card_aoi_04_01",
  "title": "井川葵 1話 この夏一番熱い場所",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――夏フェスの野外ライブ会場",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Outdoor live venue for summer festivals",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "今日は暑いね……\n炎天下で溶けちゃいそうだよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's hot today……\nI'm melting in the hot sun. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、よくこんな暑い所で踊ってられるね\n水を撒いてあげる、ほれほれ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can you all dance in such a hot place?\nI'll water it for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7000.000000000001,
          "startTime": 14.3
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_water-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7000.000000000001,
          "startTime": 14.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "どう？　水が冷たくて気持ちいい？\n……僕も浴びてみようかな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How's it feel?　Does the water feel nice and cold?\n…… I think I'll try it too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "水をかけられて喜ぶなんて子供みたいだね\nこういうのを童心に返るって言うのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're like a little kid who gets so happy of having water poured on.\nIs this what you call going back to your childhood?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "これで夏の暑さを忘れられたでしょ？　……え？\n余計に盛り上がって熱くなった？　やれやれ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now you can forget about the summer heat‚ right?　…… Eh?\nYou get extra excited‚ so even hotter?　Oh my…….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（客席に水をかけるパフォーマンス、好評みたいだな）\n（みんな濡れながらライブを楽しんでいるぞ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The performance of splashing water on the audience seems to have been well received.）\n（Everyone's getting wet and enjoying the show!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi006.m4a",
      "text": "暑いのは好きじゃないけど\n真夏の野外ライブの熱気は悪くないね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't like the heat‚\nbut the heat of an outdoor live in the middle of summer isn't so bad‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな覚悟は出来てる？\n僕達のステージをこの夏一番熱い場所にするよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "are you guys ready for that?\nWe will make our stage the hottest place this summer!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi008.m4a",
      "text": "夏の太陽よりも熱くて眩しいライブを\n目に焼き付けてよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Be sure to catch a live performance that is hotter and more dazzling\nthan the summer sun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.2955164369,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3933.3333333000055,
          "startTime": 64.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ終了後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the live",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666665999996,
          "startTime": 71.1333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.4
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ライブ、お疲れ様。パフォーマンス、盛り上がってたな\n葵の水着衣装も凄く格好良かったぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks for the live performance. Your performance‚ it was a lot of fun.\nAoi's swimsuit outfit was really cool‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi009.m4a",
      "text": "僕もやってて気持ち良かったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It felt good to do it too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi010.m4a",
      "text": "でも水をかけられて喜ぶなんて\nもしかして僕のファンは虐められるのが好きなのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But to be pleased to be doused with water‚\nperhaps my fans like to be abused?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "水着のお客さんが多かったからな……海も近いし\nみんな開放的な気分になってたんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There were a lot of customers in swimsuits……. I guess everyone\nwas feeling liberated with the ocean so close by.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi011.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだね、夏の開放感で羽目を外したくなる気持ち\n分からなくもないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Yeah‚ I can understand why the openness of summer makes you want to\ndo things unusual.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi012.m4a",
      "text": "ところで、君に折り入って話があるんだ\n今度時間を作ってくれないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ I have something to tell.\nCould you make time for me sometime?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "構わないが……今すぐじゃダメなのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind‚ but why not …… right now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi013.m4a",
      "text": "メンバーがいない所で話したいんだ\nそれじゃ、約束したからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to talk to you where the members aren't around.\nSee you then‚You promised me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.8333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2733.333333399997,
          "startTime": 121.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "葵にしては妙に真剣だったが……\nもしかして合宿で何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was oddly serious for Aoi‚ but ……\nPerhaps something happened at the camp?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 132.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "それで、一体どうしたんだ？\n何かトラブルでもあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So what is going on?\nWhat's the trouble?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi014.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに深刻な話じゃないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's not that serious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよな、この前のステージも\nかなり盛り上がってたし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know‚ the last stage\nwere pretty exciting too. ……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-aoi015.m4a",
      "text": "僕も今回のライブは手応えがあったよ\n合宿して作った新曲がかなりいい感じだったからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I‚ too‚ felt a great response on that stage.\nThe new songs we wrote at the camp were pretty good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_aoi_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば沖縄での合宿はどうだったんだ？\n俺は同行出来なかったから、ぜひ話を聞かせてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh yeah‚ how was the training camp in Okinawa?\nI couldn't go with you‚ so I'd love to hear your story.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.3666666667,
